sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor UserA as NguoiGuiLoiMoi
actor UserB as NguoiNhanLoiMoi
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant FriendSvc as FriendService
participant FriendDb as Mongo_Friend
participant Realtime as SocketService

Note over UserA,Realtime: Chặng 1 - Gửi và chấp nhận lời mời
UserA->>Client: Gửi lời mời kết bạn
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/friends/request
Gateway->>FriendSvc: Forward
FriendSvc->>FriendDb: Tạo relation pending
FriendSvc->>Realtime: Emit friend_request_sent
FriendSvc-->>Client: 201
UserB->>Client: Chấp nhận lời mời
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/friends/:friendId/accept
Gateway->>FriendSvc: Forward
FriendSvc->>FriendDb: Update accepted
FriendSvc->>Realtime: Emit accepted
